cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.LG 

The paper deals with video text detection using Fourier-Laplacian filtering and Hidden Markov Model (HMM) verification. This involves image processing, clustering, skeletonization, and classification. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by information retrieval (cs.IR) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). Multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG) are also possible categories since the paper involves video frames and HMM-based classification.
